sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Frontend
    participant Backend_API
    participant Database

    User->>Frontend: Submit Action Request
    Frontend->>Backend_API: POST /api/v1/action
    
    alt Validation Passed
        Backend_API->>Database: Transaction Request (ACID)
        Database-->>Backend_API: Commit Confirmed
        Backend_API-->>Frontend: 200 OK
        Frontend-->>User: Success Notification
    else Validation Failed
        Backend_API-->>Frontend: 400 Bad Request
        Frontend-->>User: Display Error Message
    end
    
